OL,3,CWarning over 'decade of decline' for
OL,4,Cone of England's precious chalk streams
OL,6,FThe charity is calling for more
OL,7,Fambitious environmental standards when
OL,8,Fassessing the health of what should be
OL,9,Fwildlife-rich chalk streams.
OL,11,FThe monitoring, carried out in
OL,12,Fpartnership with the Wiltshire Fishery
OL,13,FAssociation as part of the SmartRivers
OL,14,Fcitizen science project, reveals the
OL,15,Fdiversity of invertebrates fell by 17%
OL,16,Fand numbers were down by more than
OL,17,Fthree quarters (77%) in average annual
OL,18,Fcounts between 2015 and 2024.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/8
