OL,3,CWarning over 'decade of decline' for
OL,4,Cone of England's precious chalk streams
OL,6,FRiverflies are a good indicator for
OL,7,Fthe wider health of the river
OL,8,Fecosystem and are sensitive to
OL,9,Fpollution.
OL,11,FThe monitoring found that Avon's
OL,12,Friverfly species had fallen by 25% and
OL,13,Faverage abundance of the insects was
OL,14,Fdown 83% in 10 years.
OL,16,FDespite the declines, the monitored
OL,17,Fsites all scored as 'high' quality for
OL,18,Finvertebrates in 2015 and remained
OL,19,F'high' or 'good' quality in 2024.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/8
