OL,3,CWarning over 'decade of decline' for
OL,4,Cone of England's precious chalk streams
OL,6,FThese official assessments followed
OL,7,Fthe statutory water framework
OL,8,Fdirective.
OL,10,FWildFish's Dr Janina Gray warns the
OL,11,Fstatutory standards set the bar too
OL,12,Flow to reflect the high levels of
OL,13,Finvertebrate life, which a healthy
OL,14,Fchalk stream should support.
OL,16,FShe warned, if assessments show that
OL,17,Fall is well with river health, despite
OL,18,Fmajor declines in species, it makes
OL,19,Faction and investment to protect them
OL,20,Fmore difficult.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/8
