OL,3,CWarning over 'decade of decline' for
OL,4,Cone of England's precious chalk streams
OL,6,FDr Gray, head of science and policy at
OL,7,FWildFish, said: "The Avon is a Special
OL,8,FArea of Conservation (SAC), it's the
OL,9,Fmost protected river we have, and yet
OL,10,Fthe abundance drops that we're seeing
OL,11,Fare dramatic in that time period.
OL,13,F"It's just about hanging in there. It
OL,14,Fjust shows that the bar is not set
OL,15,Fhigh enough to properly protect chalk
OL,16,Fstreams.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/8
