OL,3,CWarning over 'decade of decline' for
OL,4,Cone of England's precious chalk streams
OL,6,F"These ecosystems are globally rare
OL,7,Fand ecologically critical, but without
OL,8,Fimmediate action, we risk causing
OL,9,Firreversible damage to the very
OL,10,Fcharacteristics that make them so
OL,11,Fimportant."
OL,13,FWildFish wants to see all chalk
OL,14,Fstreams should be designated as
OL,15,FSpecial Areas of Conservation (SAC),
OL,16,FWildFish argues, joining the handful
OL,17,Fof such waterways which already have
OL,18,Fthe classification.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/8
