OL,3,CWarning over 'decade of decline' for
OL,4,Cone of England's precious chalk streams
OL,6,F"We would like the Environment Agency
OL,7,Fand Natural England to revise the
OL,8,Fstandards for chalk streams to raise
OL,9,Fthe bar to protect them," Dr Gray said.
OL,11,FA spokesperson for the Department for
OL,12,FEnvironment, Food and Rural Affairs
OL,13,F(Defra) said: "Within this new
OL,14,Fgovernment, our top priority is to
OL,15,Fclean Britain's rivers and restore
OL,16,Fthem from years of damage. Chalk
OL,17,Fstream restoration is a vital part of
OL,18,Fthis effort.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/8
