OL,3,CWarning over 'decade of decline' for
OL,4,Cone of England's precious chalk streams
OL,6,F"We have secured #2 billion of funding
OL,7,Ffrom water companies to start cleaning
OL,8,Fthem, while modernising the
OL,9,Fabstraction licensing system to ensure
OL,10,Fwater is used sustainably and to stop
OL,11,Fdamaging abstraction practises to the
OL,12,Fenvironment ` a problem particularly
OL,13,Fpronounced in chalk streams.
OL,15,F"This is part of our wider plan to
OL,16,Frebuild the water system, including a
OL,17,Frecord #104 billion investment to
OL,18,Fhalve sewage spills by 2030 and the
OL,19,Fcreation of a new, powerful regulator."
